          "36 m²",
          "12.5 m²"
        ],
        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$A = \\frac{1}{2}r^2\\theta = \\frac{1}{2} \\times 36 \\times 1.2 = 18 \\times 1.2 = 21.6$ m²."
