        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$72^\\circ = \\frac{72\\pi}{180} = \\frac{2\\pi}{5}$ radians. $A = \\frac{1}{2}r^2\\theta = \\frac{1}{2} \\times 100 \\times \\frac{2\\pi}{5} = 50 \\times \\frac{2\\pi}{5} = 20\\pi$ cm²."
