        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$225^\\circ$ is in QIII, reference angle $45^\\circ$. Cosine is negative in QIII, so $\\cos 225^\\circ = -\\cos 45^\\circ = -\\frac{\\sqrt{2}}{2}$."
